OL,5, Private security patrols are being used
OL,6, to protect crops and expensive farm    
OL,7, equipment amid a rural crime wave in   
OL,8, England and Wales, the BBC has learned.
OL,10,FFarmers have told the BBC that police  
OL,11,Frarely solve rural offences and are not
OL,12,Fdoing enough to tackle organised crime.
OL,14,FSuspects are almost 25% more likely to 
OL,15,Fbe charged for crimes in urban areas   
OL,16,Fthan in the countryside, BBC analysis  
OL,17,Fof data has found.                     
OL,19,FThe Home Office says forces plan to    
OL,20,Ftackle the "challenges" of rural crime.
